{"id":232951896,"title":"檸檬瑪德蓮 Lemon Madeleine 做法 食譜","content":"祝大家新年快樂，這次分享的食譜是經典的法式小蛋糕-瑪德蓮，材料不會太麻煩，步驟也算簡單，過年在家沒事可以動手做做看，跟親朋好友一起分享這美味的小點心~\n\n影片版：https://youtu.be/ht7s-Rin_WA\n\n材料： 奶油 200g、全蛋 3顆、砂糖 150g、中筋麵粉 185g、泡打粉7.5 g、牛奶 55mL、檸檬汁 60mL、糖粉 150g \n\n步驟：\n1. 用小火將奶油煮到融化，備用\n2. 將雞蛋和砂糖攪拌至淺黃色\n3. 蛋液中加入過篩好的麵粉和泡打粉，攪拌到看不見粉類顆粒狀\n4. 分兩次加入牛奶，攪拌均勻\n5. 加入融化奶油，攪拌均勻\n6. 麵糊放入冰箱，冷藏至少30分鐘\n7. 模具塗上一層奶油，再撒上麵粉，預防脫模時沾黏\n8. 取出冷藏好的麵糊，倒入模具內，約8分滿\n9. 烤箱預熱180℃，烤12-15分鐘，烤完後取出放涼\n10. 混合檸檬汁和糖粉成檸檬糖霜\n11. 放涼的瑪德蓮表面沾上檸檬糖霜，再進烤箱用200℃烤2分鐘，收乾糖霜水份","excerpt":"祝大家新年快樂，這次分享的食譜是經典的法式小蛋糕-瑪德蓮，材料不會太麻煩，步驟也算簡單，過年在家沒事可以動手做做看，跟親朋好友一起分享這美味的小點心~，影片版：材料： 奶油 200g、全蛋 3顆、砂糖","anonymousSchool":false,"anonymousDepartment":false,"pinned":false,"forumId":"de977130-f3eb-467b-822e-b0e91124e9eb","replyId":null,"createdAt":"2020-01-24T15:38:54.399Z","updatedAt":"2020-01-24T16:07:16.844Z","commentCount":2,"likeCount":12,"tags":[],"topics":["瑪德蓮","做法","食譜","甜點","美食"],"supportedReactions":null,"withNickname":true,"reportReason":"","hiddenByAuthor":false,"meta":{"layout":"classic"},"forumName":"美食","forumAlias":"food","school":"9巷5弄","department":"alley5lane9","replyTitle":null,"gender":"M","personaSubscriptable":false,"reactions":[{"id":"286f599c-f86a-4932-82f0-f5a06f1eca03","count":12}],"hidden":false,"customStyle":null,"isSuspiciousAccount":false,"layout":"classic","withImages":false,"withVideos":false,"media":[],"reportReasonText":"","mediaMeta":[{"id":"8cca0f88-7640-44e0-a208-92e4acfc9518","url":"https://img.youtube.com/vi/ht7s-Rin_WA/hqdefault.jpg","normalizedUrl":"https://img.youtube.com/vi/ht7s-Rin_WA/hqdefault.jpg","thumbnail":"https://img.youtube.com/vi/ht7s-Rin_WA/hqdefault.jpg","type":"image/thumbnail","tags":["ANNOTATED"],"createdAt":"2020-01-24T15:38:54.399Z","updatedAt":"2020-01-24T16:07:16.844Z"},{"id":"8cca0f88-7640-44e0-a208-92e4acfc9518","url":"https://youtu.be/ht7s-Rin_WA","normalizedUrl":"https://www.youtube.com/watch?v=ht7s-Rin_WA","thumbnail":"https://img.youtube.com/vi/ht7s-Rin_WA/hqdefault.jpg","type":"